    <tags>music downloader terminal tui cli audio flac</tags>
    <summary>Blazing-fast TUI music downloader written in pure C</summary>
    <description>
SquidGet is a blazing-fast terminal-based music downloader with a beautiful text-based user interface.
Built entirely in C for maximum performance, it allows you to search, download, and manage your music collection
directly from the command line. Features include album downloads, metadata tagging, and support for high-quality
audio formats.

Features:
- Fast TUI-based music downloading
- Album and track support
- Metadata tagging
- Cross-platform support
- Desktop shortcut creation
    </description>
    <releaseNotes>Initial release of SquidGet!
- Fast TUI-based music downloading
- Album and track support
- Metadata tagging
- Cross-platform support
- Desktop shortcut support</releaseNotes>
